HEADWORD: homestretch
<hw>homestretch</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the straight segment
of a racetrack leading to the finish line.</def> <wns>[wns=1]</wns>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <mark>[fig.]</mark> <def>The last
or concluding part of any extended activity that has a definite
conclusion; the final phase of any activity; <as>as, the election was
neck-and-neck in the <ex>homestretch</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>home town</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>hometown</ent>⟦br⟧
